        <briefdescription>
<para>Computes total remaining processing time for a job from <computeroutput>op</computeroutput> onward. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Sums durations from <computeroutput>op.op_index</computeroutput> to the end of the job&apos;s operation list. Used as the sort key for <ref refid="mirror__des_8py_1a9e69b7fc7cddb1c2fd72d11f79aeec49" kindref="member">rule_mwr</ref>. Mirrors C# <computeroutput>DispatchingRules.RemainingWork</computeroutput>.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>op</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The reference operation whose index marks the start of summation. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>jobs</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The full job list used to retrieve the owning job&apos;s operations. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Total remaining duration including <computeroutput>op</computeroutput> itself. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
